data.description: This is a MUST SEE for all these reasons and more: over 1800 finished square feet, unique layout, amazing basement to entertain, walkout, includes all appliances (plus washer/dryer), new AC, on .34 lot, AND 1 block from the airport!  You'll feel right at home as you step inside into the family room - it's arched doorways and white fireplace with wood mantel show off its character!  The kitchen has a quaint eat in area - if you need more space for a table for 4+, there is a great dining room off the kitchen.  This room could be a multi-purpose room if needed with a door to the deck.  There are 2 bedrooms on the main with a full bath.  The lower level walkout is the true show stopper...a dance floor/music area, non conforming bedroom, spacious family room, 3/4 bath, laundry room.  The backyard is fabulous with a deck, patio and a great backyard with several trees for privacy. You don't want to miss out on this home - it just might be the one!
